3>\nThe center of any central mix concrete batching plant is the mixer. There are several types of mixers available on a ready mix plant: drum tilt mixer, reversing drum mixer, twin shaft horizontal mixer also known as a compulsory mixer and planetary mixer as well as pan and turbine mixers.  Depending on the application required, concrete batch plant operations can be designed to produce ready mixed concrete, concrete blocks, architectural concrete products, precast concrete, prestressed concrete, structural bridge members, and even concrete light poles.  Most batch plants store different stones, sand and cements for the types of concrete that each plant is capable of producing. They create unique mixes to deliver customized performance suitable for each construction need. Through extensive research, Ready Mix Producers utilize innovative mix designs to produce performance concretes.\n<h2>Trends in Concrete Batch Plants</h2>\nThe other type of concrete batching plant which is rapidly gaining popularity and can be seen widely used in construction sites, is called the Mobile (or Portable) Batching Plant. The mobile batching units include the structure which carries the batchers, conveyors, scales, control equipment and small silos to be used at the construction site. They provide a lot of cost and time savings and increase efficiency at the building site.\n\nWith the advent of technology, most modern  batch plants use computer aided control to assist in the quick and accurate measurement of ingredients, as well as to coordinate the functioning of various parts and accessories for safe operation. Since the quality and performance of concrete is highly dependent on the water content, these sophisticated systems will use moisture probes to gauge the amount of water that is part of the aggregate (sand and rock) material during weighing.  If there is a need for changing the water content, it can be programmed to automatically do so.\n\nConcrete is the most used manmade material in the world, with nearly three tons used annually for each man, woman and child. Concrete has been around for centuries and is an integral part of every civilization. The ancient Romans first used primitive mixes of sand, gravel, lime and gypsum to create enduring concrete structures, such as the Pantheon, that are still standing today. Concrete technology in the modern age has dramatically improved. Ready Mix Producers manufacture concrete in state-of-the-art plants that utilize sophisticated computers to accurately batch the correct proportions of ingredients to create a consistent, high-quality product.','Concrete Batch Plants','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave','','','2011-06-19 18:44:15','2011-06-19 18:44:15','',2,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/?p=4',0,'revision','',0),(11,1,'2011-05-04 15:59:56','2011-05-04 15:59:56','','Auto Draft','','inherit','open','open','','3-revision','','','2011-05-04 15:59:56','2011-05-04 15:59:56','',3,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/3-revision',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2011-05-04 15:59:32','2011-05-04 15:59:32','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n\r\n...or something like this:\r\n\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\n\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision','','','2011-05-04 15:59:32','2011-05-04 15:59:32','',2,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/2-revision',0,'revision','',0),(5,1,'2011-05-28 17:35:14','2011-05-28 17:35:14','<h1>MOBILE BATCH PLANTS</h1>\r\nWith the introduction of mobile batch plants as a response to burgeoning demand for concrete due to an increase in construction, concrete producers continuously responded with innovative solutions to cater to the requirements of clients. Any small difference in the quality of material supplied or any delays in transportation could be very costly for both client and producer. However, with the advent of <strong>mobile batch plants</strong> or mobile batching plants, there has been a great increase in the quality of concrete supplied and delivery times have also been reduced significantly.  In addition, the mobile batch plant allows the producer to move quickly and efficiently around a large site or transport the entire operation to a new site in a matter of hours in many cases.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-148\" title=\"mobile-batch-plants\" src=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/mobile-batch-plants.jpg\" alt=\"mobile batch plants\" width=\"320\" height=\"150\" />\r\n<h2>What are mobile batch plants?</h2>\r\nUnlike conventional batching plants mobile plants can be transported from site to site with minimal set-up time. Earlier, engineers made use of mobile placing booms as well as truck-mounted concrete pumps. Apart from this they had no other option to get concrete on site. The most commonly used method was using plants in the city for mixing and then transporting the concrete onto the construction site via mixer trucks.\r\n<h3>Advantage of mobile batch plants</h3>\r\nHowever, since concrete is sensitive to time and heat, spending too much time on the road results in a significant loss of quality.\r\n\r\nThey are reliable due to the high level of technology involved in producing them and provide accurate results. Mobile batching plants can work in a wide range of environmental conditions and give their maximum potential.\r\n\r\nAnother benefit of mobile batching plants is that they can be quickly adjusted according to the requirements of the job. Since the batching is done at the construction site itself, the adjustments can be done swiftly in a matter of seconds by adjusting the plant or mix design.\r\n\r\nCompanies need a highly functional mobile batch plant so that the processes can be completed to the best standards. Even a  minor failure to detect the requirements properly can cost a company  immensely. A quality mobile concrete batch plant is the base to build your a highly mobile workforce for any producer.\r\n\r\nIf you are thinking that selecting a mobile concrete batch plant is a very easy  task then let me tell you that the decision relating to the upgrading,  replacing or buying of a new mobile concrete plant is indeed a very challenging  task. In fact even the senior most batch plant operators can be seen  baffled when decision related to batching plants needs to be taken. It would be beneficial to consult a highly experienced equipment dealer like Gulf Atlantic Industrial Equipment, Inc. before making such a critical investment.\r\n\r\nOverall, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">mobile batching plants</span> have been a welcome addition to the line of batching plants available as they have low operational costs and can be quickly adjusted according to <a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: black;\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Construction\">construction</a> site requirements.\r\n\r\nRelated articles:<a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/products-portable-concrete-batch-plants.php\"></a>\r\n\r\n<address><a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/products-portable-concrete-batch-plants.php\">portable concrete batch plants </a>\r\n</address> <address>concrete batch plants</address> <address>batch plant mixer</address> <address>pug mills\r\n</address>','Mobile Batch Plants','','publish','open','open','','mobile-batch-plants','','','2011-06-19 18:13:03','2011-06-19 18:13:03','',0,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/?p=5',0,'post','',1),(6,1,'2011-05-10 19:25:10','2011-05-10 19:25:10','This is where first article goes','Mobile atch plants','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision','','','2011-05-10 19:25:10','2011-05-10 19:25:10','',5,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/5-revision',0,'revision','',0),(7,1,'2011-05-12 16:08:50','2011-05-12 16:08:50','','Comanche-Products-concrete-batch-plant','Comanche Products Concrete Batch Plant','inherit','open','open','','comanche-products-concrete-batch-plant','','','2011-05-12 16:08:50','2011-05-12 16:08:50','',2,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Comanche-Products-concrete-batch-plant.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(10,1,'2011-05-12 17:31:50','2011-05-12 17:31:50','[caption id=\"attachment_7\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"491\" caption=\"Comanche Products Concrete Batch Plant\"]<a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Comanche-Products-concrete-batch-plant.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-7\" title=\"Comanche-Products-concrete-batch-plant\" src=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Comanche-Products-concrete-batch-plant.jpg\" alt=\"concrete batch plant\" width=\"491\" height=\"434\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis is a sample page - test only -\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Concrete Batch Plants Examples','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-3','','','2011-05-12 17:31:50','2011-05-12 17:31:50','',2,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/2-revision-3',0,'revision','',0),(14,1,'2011-05-16 15:47:06','2011-05-16 15:47:06','The Federal Highway Administrati