as  mobile features as well as the adaptability to working site features.  This type of recycle crusher too comes in two styles, Hydraulic Driven track  mobile plant and Crawler type mobile crushers.','Recycle Crusher','','inherit','open','open','','66-revision-5','','','2011-06-27 17:14:16','2011-06-27 17:14:16','',66,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/66-revision-5',0,'revision','',0),(53,1,'2011-06-08 18:00:46','2011-06-08 18:00:46','<strong> </strong><strong>Portable concrete plants</strong> allow builders to produce concrete for the project at the construction site itself instead of having to order it at a fixed concrete plant site and then transport it at a heavy cost. Instead of being loaded at a distant site, the raw materials, along with water are discharged to the mixer truck on the construction site. Portable concrete plants, like normal concrete batch plants, use the same batch systems and equipment produce concrete. The concrete developed in concrete batch plants as well as portable concrete batch plants are used for foundations, paving material for roads, parking lots, tilt-up walls, poured in place, precast and prestressed.\r\n<h1><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-139\" title=\"portable-concrete-plants\" src=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/portable-concrete-plants.jpg\" alt=\"portable concrete plants\" width=\"330\" height=\"269\" />Portable Concrete Plants</h1>\r\nThe main purpose of portable concrete plants has been to provide affordable and single unit with highway affordability, while keeping a low profile and a minimum amount of set-up time. These portable plants have reduced many a headache for construction site managers because they are very efficient in production and at the same time easy to use and handle. The main purpose of a portable concrete batch plant is to reduce time and expenses.  By removing the travel time required from a stationary concrete batch plant over long distances to a job site, a portable concrete batch plant allows producers the flexibility to complete projects in remote locations, move the batch plant to another site quickly upon project completion, and permitting issues are greatly reduced or eliminated.\r\n<h2>Portable Concrete Plants - general nature</h2>\r\nPortable <a style=\"text-decoration: none; color: black;\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concrete\">concrete</a> plants have been developed to ease the complete process of mixing and manufacturing ready mix concrete. Most portable concrete plants are self erecting and can be constantly moved and transported throughout the construction site or site to site according to the requirements of the contractor. The entire structure and components of portable concrete batch plant must be sturdy enough to handle the continuous transportation from one place to another. When built with the proper engineering, the portable concrete batch plant performs at its best and exceeds customers’ expectations.\r\n<h3>Range of Portable Concrete Plants</h3>\r\nThere is a whole range of portable concrete plants available to fit the budget constraints of different customers. Starting from the design and specification stages to the manufacturing and installation and commissioning of a portable concrete plant, all top manufacturers take the necessary steps to make sure the final product is up to the mark and does not cause any problems for the client.\r\n\r\nPortable concrete plants can also be customized as per requirements of clients and customers. Full account of available space and existing equipments is taken into consideration in order to deliver dynamic solutions. Another important aspect is that if the requirement is not long term, the portable concrete batch plant or concrete batch plants can be rented as well.\r\n\r\nWhen purchasing a portable concrete batch plant, factors to consider include:  overall travel height, whether or not the batch plant is truly \"self-erecting\" or will require the use of a crane, and yards per hour of productivity that will be required to complete a project.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Related Articles:</strong>\r\n\r\n<address><a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com\">Concrete Batch Plants</a></address> <address><a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/mobile-batch-plants\">Mobile Batch Plants</a></address> <address><a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/ready-mix-plants\">Ready Mix Plants</a></address> <address><a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/batch-plant-mixer\">Batch Plant Mixers</a>\r\n</address>For more detailed information and brands contact <a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/products-portable-concrete-batch-plants.php#apachesqp\">portable concrete plants</a>','Portable Concrete Plants','','publish','open','open','','portable-concrete-plants','','\nhttp://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/mobile-batch-plants','2011-06-21 16:41:37','2011-06-21 16:41:37','',0,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/?p=53',0,'post','',1),(54,1,'2011-05-16 21:32:22','2011-05-16 21:32:22','','Portable Concrete Plants','','inherit','open','open','','53-revision','','','2011-05-16 21:32:22','2011-05-16 21:32:22','',53,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/53-revision',0,'revision','',0),(191,1,'2011-06-06 21:29:56','2011-06-06 21:29:56','<strong></strong><strong>Portable concrete plants</strong> allow builders to produce concrete for the project at the construction site itself instead of having to order it at a fixed concrete plant site and then transport it at a heavy cost. Instead of being loaded at a distant site, the raw materials, along with water are discharged to the mixer truck on the construction site. Portable concrete plants, like normal concrete batch plants, use the same batch systems and equipment produce concrete. The concrete developed in concrete batch plants as well as portable concrete batch plants are used for foundations, paving material