n•    For concrete equipment, preventative care is essential for good  use. It is necessary to pressure wash, check and adjust the equipment as  needed. Some contractors may buy used equipment because the costs of  mixers, pumps and other equipment is quite high. However, a breakdown in  equipment may irritate customers and cause a contractor to lose a  valuable contract. New equipment may be worth the cost for its  reliability factor and manufacturer\'s warranty.\n\n<address>For more information on purchasing <a href=\"../../\" target=\"_blank\">concrete batch plants </a>\n</address> <address>More information on <a title=\"portable concrete plants\" href=\"../portable-concrete-plants\">portable concrete plants</a></address> <address>More information on <a href=\"http://http//www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/mobile-batch-plant\">mobile match plant</a></address> <address> </address>More information on <a title=\"batch plant mixers\" href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com\">batch plant mixer</a>\n<div id=\"suggestions\">\n<div id=\"suggestions\">\n<ul>\n	<li>You definitely want to include an image and set the alt tag to your keyword.</li>\n	<li>You should point a link to your other pages with keyword as anchor text.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n&nbsp;','Batch Plant Mixer','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-10','','','2011-06-13 20:14:56','2011-06-13 20:14:56','',46,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/46-revision-10',0,'revision','',0),(236,1,'2011-06-13 20:16:34','2011-06-13 20:16:34','A <strong>batch plant mixer</strong> is usually used when it comes to using ready-mixed  concrete. This is because it saves a lot of time and is ideal with large  projects. It originated from the 1940s, when the world was trying to  build back after the war, and is still popular in many building projects  now. The batch plant mixer is perfect to be used in small spaces and for larger commercial projects. R&amp;S Industries manufacturers precision engineered Central