n track  mobile plant and Crawler type mobile crushers</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<address>For more information on purchasing a <a title=\"Recycle Crusher\" href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com\" target=\"_blank\">recycle crusher</a> contact Gulf Atlantic Equipment<br />\r\n</address>\r\n<address>Click here for more information on <a title=\"portable concrete plants\" href=\"../portable-concrete-plants\">portable concrete plants</a> and how you might obtain one</address>\r\n<address>Click here for more information on <a href=\"http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com\" target=\"_blank\">concrete batch plant suppliers</a> and your project needs</address>\r\n','Recycle Crusher','','inherit','open','open','','66-revision-19','','','2011-06-27 20:59:02','2011-06-27 20:59:02','',66,'http://www.gulfatlanticequipment.com/blog/66-revision-19',0,'revision','',0),(301,1,'2011-07-07 17:07:11','2011-07-07 17:07:11','RCC is short for Roller Compacted Concrete which is a blend of concrete  which is similar to the usual concrete but just has a different ratio of  ingredients used in it. The ingredients used include cement, water and  aggregates but RCC tends to be drier and more rigid in nature than the  normal concrete that you may find. It is generally very stiff by  temperament and hence requires to be completely mixed before it can be  discharged. An RCC Mixer has specifically been designed to do this and to  convert any dry batch plant into a central mix and RCC plant.\n<h1>Types of RCC Mixers</h1>\nThere are various different RCC mixers made by several companies but the  two important ones with some advanced features and benefits include the  following:\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Rapid International Model 400C</strong> and <strong> </strong>Continuous Mixing Plants - available either volumetric or weighed processing.</li>\n	<li><strong>Sicoma Mao 6000 Twin Shaft mixer</strong> mounted on a stationary or portable concrete batch plant.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Some of the advanced features o